description:
Sander Bos discovered that Byobu incorrectly handled certain Apport data.
An attacker could possibly use this issue to expose sensitive information.

byobu.description: text window manager, shell multiplexer, integrated DevOps environ

title: Byobu vulnerability
action: In general, a standard system update will make all the necessary changes.
isummary: Byobu could be made to expose sensitive information.
